body:
@nsivabalan 
Hello Sivabalan, 
sorry for disturbance, but we really need your help to approve our first PR so that we could submit further materials for the RFC discussed in the dev-maillist. Could you please help us to approve? Thanks so much :)

@hudi-bot run azure

`@hudi-bot run azure`

`run azure`

@hudi-bot run azure

`@hudi-bot run azure`

`run azure`

Finally I resolved the problem, thank you for your  help @KnightChess 
@nsivabalan @yihua I think this mistake should be corrected in the official documentation and 
It's necessary to remind users to disable ```hive.metastore.disallow.incompatible.col.type.changes``` in hive metastore

@gtwuser   pls try add 
            "hoodie.schema.on.read.enable" -> "true",
            "hoodie.datasource.write.reconcile.schema" -> "true",

@hudi-bot run azure

`@hudi-bot run azure`

`run azure`

